ton to load the builder</li>\r\n 	<li>Click the gray folder icon and select the header template to import, select your menu in the nav element and click Update.</li>\r\n 	<li>Repeat for Footer</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Help &amp; Support</h3>\r\nThese instructions are for those of you who just want to download themes and install them yourself. Our basic service includes installing it to your domain and hosting. So please order our basic service and we will install it for you.', 'array(\r\n        \"id\" 		 => \"Castify-Audio\",\r\n        \"url\" 		 => \"https://templatekit.jegtheme.com/castify/\",\r\n        \"purchase\" 	 => \"/downloads/castify-audio-podcast-theme/\",\r\n        \"responsive\" => \"yes\",\r\n        \"type\"       => \"wordpress\",\r\n        \"thumb\"      => \"\"\r\n    ),'),
(22, 'CookBlog – Food & Personal Blog Theme', 'CookBlog-babiato-@TingTung', 'Cookblog-Food', 'https://www.closecrowds.com/wp-admin/post.php?post=6821&action=edit', '/downloads/cookblog-food-personal-blog-theme/', 'https://closecrowds.com/themes/?theme=Cookblog-Food', 'https://elements.envato.com/cookblog-food-personal-blog-elementor-template-kit-6TNQW8Y', 'https://kit.baliniz.com/cookblog/?storefront=envato-elements', 15, 'Blog,Blogging,Cook,Cooking,Fashion,Feminine,Food,Food Blog,Journal,Lifestyle,Magazine,Personal,Personal Blog,Recipe,Travel,', '', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1iU6C7q3D0xCjTaGen8rUhCgGMoj-keLF/view?usp=sharing', '<p>CookBlog is a stunning modern food blogging Elementor Theme to create a pro-level and functional website for a food blog, cooking recipe, personal &amp; travel blog, and any kind of blogging website.</p>\r\n<p>This Theme includes carefully crafted 15+ stunning templates. You can build your professional, modern, and functional WordPress blog website just a click away and without coding.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>Elementor Pro required</li>\r\n    <li>Modern &amp; Elegant Design</li>\r\n    <li>15+ Templates with Global Theme Style</li>\r\n    <li>Fully Responsive Layout</li>\r\n    <li>Retina Ready</li>\r\n    <li>Fully Customizable</li>\r\n    <li>Cross Browser Compatibility: Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Opera</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br></p>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n<h2>Instruction</h2>\r\n<h3>How to Use Themes:</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Install and Activate the \"Envato Elements\" plugin from Plugins &gt; Add New in WordPress</li>\r\n 	<li>Download your themes file and Do not unzip</li>\r\n 	<li>In WordPress, go to Elements &gt; Installed themes and click <strong>Upload Theme Zip File</strong>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-6132\" src=\"https://www.closecrowds.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screenshot-on-2021-02-15-at-15_58_20-277x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"277\" height=\"300\"></li>\r\n 	<li>Check