ilder</li>\r\n 	<li>Click the gray folder icon and select the header template to import, select your menu in the nav element and click Update.</li>\r\n 	<li>Repeat for Footer</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h3>Help &amp; Support</h3>\r\nThese instructions are for those of you who just want to download themes and install them yourself. Our basic service includes installing it to your domain and hosting. So please order our basic service and we will install it for you.', 'array(\r\n        \"id\" 		 => \"Cookblog-Food\",\r\n        \"url\" 		 => \"https://kit.baliniz.com/cookblog/?storefront=envato-elements\",\r\n        \"purchase\" 	 => \"/downloads/cookblog-food-personal-blog-theme/\",\r\n        \"responsive\" => \"yes\",\r\n        \"type\"       => \"wordpress\",\r\n        \"thumb\"      => \"\"\r\n    ),'),
