(101, 'Drago - Creative Digital Agency Theme', 'Drago-babiato-@TingTung', 'drago-creative', 'https://www.closecrowds.com/wp-admin/post.php?post=7374&action=edit', '/downloads/drago-creative-digital-agency-theme/', 'https://closecrowds.com/themes/?theme=Drago-Creative', 'https://elements.envato.com/drago-creative-digital-agency-elementor-template-k-XJTWJZN', 'https://drago-elementor.42theme.com/', 19, 'Advertising,Agency,Clean,Corporate Agency,Creative,Creative Agency,Design,Freelancer,Marketing Agency,Modern,Multipurpose Agency,Portfolio,Responsive,Startup Business', '', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1mMLrowsC-zyorXTiJ7nnqjAQi1p-5BKN/view?usp=sharing', '<p>Drago is Elementor Theme build for a creative and digital studio to showcase their portfolio and services. This template contains all the pages required for a creative digital studio. It is a fully responsive and cross-browser compatible template. This Theme is built with Elementor Pro. Drago is an Elementor Theme perfectly suits for Digital agency, Portfolio, Startup business, and Marketing landing page websites. Its design is up to modern design trends. You can ready to use this template for a design agency or business purposes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>/ <strong>We recommend this Theme for the following websites:</strong> *Digital Agency *Creative Agency *Marketing Agency *Design Studios *Digital Marketing Agencies *And other business service websites</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Getting started with the template is extremely simple &ndash; install the template on your website, select a page, and start editing with the Elementor. The template is completely ready for use and you do not need to make any additional settings on your WordPress website. Drago Theme is a perfect choice for those who want to create a trendy and modern website.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With 50 page and section templates available, you&rsquo;ll have your new website ready in no time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*True zero coding: styles and effects are done within the Elementor panel.